{"tid":2255441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報中國可使用柬埔寨軍事基地，柬埔寨民眾到中國使館外抗議","createTime":"2020-10-23T14:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T22:55:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"386b0b3ac699800d416df313a7f2763a057af211","tid":2255441,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556379-20201023.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556379-20201023.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=36d02573\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556379-20201023.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=422189aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556379-20201023.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨有民眾到中國駐當地大使館附近示威，抗議有報道指中國獲准使用當地一個軍事基地。警方拘留數名示威者問話。<br />\n<br />\n在首都金邊，示威者揮動柬埔寨國旗，高叫「拒絕中國軍隊在柬埔寨存在」等口號。警方表示，集會活動並未取得許可，當局有需要保護大使館，以及維持公共秩序，利用揚聲器呼籲示威者限時散去。路透社報道，有警員要求現場採訪的記者刪除拍攝到的部分相片及影片。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，柬埔寨容許中國增強在當地的影響力，以換取經濟支援，金邊政府一直堅稱外交和安全政策獨立，多次否認與北京達成秘密協議，批准解放軍使用境內一個海軍基地。"},{"pid":"63bbea2fdd7a48376dfe629ade04bb06bd449e27","tid":2255441,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"可以預計中國未來點樣統治全世界了 不停靠玩滲透去統治人地國家"},{"pid":"8f880ef3fd8cf6825808da88293983714429393f","tid":2255441,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"當年中共指使赤柬屠殺幾百萬柬埔寨人, 好快歷史重演"},{"pid":"b3f068e28159da6f8b8296d51d4b00cbfbeaa933","tid":2255441,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"一路幫開香港既澳洲手足Drew Pavlou眾籌緊,仲差3000usd.請大家幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/drew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fdrew-pa